PN,40201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FProtesters have a responsibility to
OL,8,Fcall out those chanting "globalise the
OL,9,Fintifada" at Gaza marches, the prime
OL,10,Fminister has said, amid growing
OL,11,Fconcerns about high levels of
OL,12,Fantisemitism in the UK.
OL,14,FKeir Starmer stated that there should
OL,15,Fbe "tougher action" in relation to
OL,16,Fpeople using such phrases and urged
OL,17,Fpeople to stop and ask themselves why
OL,18,Fthey were not calling it out.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,F"I will defend the right of peaceful
OL,8,Fprotest very strongly and freedom of
OL,9,Fspeech," the prime minister told the
OL,10,FBBC Radio 4's Today programme on
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,13,F"I have defended those principles all
OL,14,Fmy life and I will continue to do so.
OL,15,FAnd so I'm not stepping back from that
OL,16,Fone bit.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,F"But if you are on a march or a
OL,8,Fprotest where people are chanting,
OL,9,F'globalise the Intifada', you do have
OL,10,Fto stop and ask yourself, why am I not
OL,11,Fcalling this out? Why am I on a march
OL,12,Fwhere this is the chant? And I do
OL,13,Fthink it's time for people just to ask
OL,14,Fthemselves that."
OL,16,F"I'm not saying, of course, that there
OL,17,Faren't very strong legitimate views
OL,18,Fabout the Middle East, about Gaza. We
OL,19,Fall have deep concerns about it.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,F"This Government has recognised
OL,8,FPalestine just last year. So, of
OL,9,Fcourse, there are important issues."
OL,11,FStarmer said asked that people
OL,12,Fattending protests "reflect" on what
OL,13,Fthe Jewish community is going through,
OL,14,Fstating that the "cumulative" effect
OL,15,Fof repeated marches is a concern.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FHe said he was not in favour of
OL,8,Fbanning the marches as a whole, but
OL,9,Finstead suggested a "whole of society
OL,10,Fresponse" was needed to draw attention
OL,11,Fto antisemitism, alongside "further
OL,12,Fpowers" to police demonstrations.
OL,14,FStarmer's words come as the head of
OL,15,Fthe Met Police warned that Britain's
OL,16,FJewish community are currently facing
OL,17,Fa "ghastly Venn diagram" of hate from
OL,18,Fall sides following a spate of
OL,19,Fantisemitic attacks.
OL,26,@qD@UOUrD@IO]sD@\OUtD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FThe UK terrorism threat level has been
OL,8,Fraised to "severe" by the Joint
OL,9,FTerrorism Analysis Centre, meaning a
OL,10,Fterror attack is "highly likely",
OL,11,Fafter two Jewish men were stabbed in
OL,12,FGolders Green on Wednesday.
OL,14,FBoth men injured in the Golders Green
OL,15,Fattack have now been discharged from
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@RO]rD@ROUrD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FSuspect Essa Suleiman, 45, has been
OL,8,Fcharged with attempting to kill
OL,9,FShloime Rand, 34, and Norman Shine,
OL,10,F76, along with a third man, Ishmail
OL,11,FHussein, who was targeted earlier the
OL,12,Fsame day.
OL,14,FMet Police Commissioner Mark Rowley
OL,15,Fsaid the Jewish community are the
OL,16,F"centre of gravity of so many
OL,17,Fideologies" on Saturday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,F"Every racist or extremist or
OL,8,Fterrorist group has a list of people
OL,9,Fthey hate because they all create an
OL,10,F'other' who they want to blame
OL,11,Feverything on and visit everything
OL,12,Fon," Rowley told The Times.
OL,14,F"The ghastly fact is that Jews are on
OL,15,Feverybody's list, all of those hateful
OL,16,Fgroups, whether you're extreme right,
OL,17,Fwhether you're extreme left, whether
OL,18,Fyou're Islamist terrorist, whether
OL,19,Fyou're right-wing terrorist, and some
OL,20,Fhostile states as well now with some
OL,21,Fsort of Iranian-related threats."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FRowley said he believed social media
OL,8,Fhas brought antisemitic views into the
OL,9,Fmainstream, describing it as an
OL,10,F"epidemic" that is causing a greater
OL,11,Fthreat to the Jewish community than
OL,12,Fever before.
OL,14,F"If you overlay three things now -
OL,15,Fhate crime, terrorism and hostile
OL,16,Fstate activity - you add all that
OL,17,Ftogether, that combined effect with
OL,18,Fthat building of ideology online, it
OL,19,Fis really dangerous and troubling,"
OL,20,FRowley said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,F"Jewish communities feel that: you can
OL,8,Fsee that in how they talk, how it's
OL,9,Fmaking them change their lives. That's
OL,10,Fan appalling state of affairs."
OL,12,FThe Golders Green stabbings are just
OL,13,Fthe latest in a series of antisemitic
OL,14,Fattacks in Britain in recent weeks.
OL,16,FOn March 23, four Hatzola ambulances,
OL,17,Frun by the Jewish community, were set
OL,18,Falight in Golders Green, causing gas
OL,19,Fcanisters stored in the vehicles to
OL,20,Fexplode.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FThree weeks later a brick was thrown
OL,8,Fat the Finchley Reform Synagogue, also
OL,9,Fin north London, before the Kenton
OL,10,FUnited Synagogue in Harrow, west
OL,11,FLondon, was targeted with "some sort
OL,12,Fof accelerant".
OL,14,FRowley said he had requested urgent
OL,15,Ffunding to recruit 300 officers to
OL,16,Fprotect the Jewish community, with
OL,17,Fplans for a dedicated group of police
OL,18,Fto patrol north west London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FHe also defended the two officers who
OL,8,Fdetained the suspect in the Golders
OL,9,FGreen attack, as footage shared on
OL,10,Fsocial media appeared to show them
OL,11,Fkicking the suspect in the head while
OL,12,Fhe held onto the knife.
OL,14,F"One of the Taser shots has connected
OL,15,Fbut he's still not giving up the
OL,16,Fknife. It's pretty obvious the sort of
OL,17,Fsuspicion they're going to have that
OL,18,Fhe may have an explosive device,"
OL,19,FRowley said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777903640
OL,3,CProtesters have duty to call out
OL,4,C'globalise the intifada' chants, says
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FHe said he had spoken to the officers
OL,8,Ftwo hours after the incident took
OL,9,Fplace, adding: "It's very traumatic
OL,10,Ffor them. They've got to live with
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FRowley and Starmer were both critical
OL,14,Fof Green Party leader Zack Polanski
OL,15,Fafter he reshared a social media post
OL,16,Fthat said the officers at the scene
OL,17,Facted "violently".
OL,19,FPolanski has since apologised for
OL,20,F"sharing a tweet in haste" and invited
OL,21,FRowley to meet with him.
OL,26,@qD@POUsD@FO]yD@GOUyD@QO]|D@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
